==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Re-build
<hw>Re-build"</hw></mhw>
<pr>(r⟦emac⟧*b⟦icr⟧ld")</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To build again, as
something which has been demolished; to construct anew; <as>as, to
<ex>rebuild</ex> a house, a wall, a wharf, or a city</as>. Usually used
without the hyphen.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> build anew, build again, reconstruct,
reerect.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> + <source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rebuilder</ent>⟦br⟧
